##Wuhan, these days the sanitation workers

Weiweiao999

Introduction, hello, I am Li Wei Ao, thank you for your attention. Note: It may take a month or two to update this post, or even longer

Today (March 6,2020) , in the construction of the third road in Qingshan District, Wuhan, Wuhan, saw a few big sister sanitation workers, making brooms.

I asked them, why do they have to make their own brooms?

The answer was: only bamboo leaves..

It was the first time I'd ever seen anything like it, and I was amazed.

I also think of some of the most common occupational groups I have seen on the streets of Wuhan -- Foshan -- since the beginning of February, more than a month ago: deliverymen (including food delivery) , police officers, sanitation workers.

The number one, no doubt, is sanitation workers -- whether it's sunny or rainy, windy or snowy, I see them every day.

I don't know if they have the freedom to choose not to come out to work, but it can be seen that the streets of Wuhan are always clean these days.

I take these days of the sanitation workers, tidy up, is also "Wuhan, these days of the street" (four) bar.

(1) Wuhan, the streets and alleys these days; (2) Wuhan, the streets and alleys these days; (3) Wuhan, the streets and alleys these days

6 March

Overcast sky

On the third road of construction, the sanitation workers who are weaving brooms.

On the other side of the road is the Kaiyuan mansion that shouted "fake, fake" to the vice premier yesterday, March 5,2020.

5 March

It's a beautiful day

On Wuluo road, the masters who are emptying the garbage can.

Again, for the first time:

The garbage can is hung on the garbage truck, and then it can dump the garbage automatically.

On the bridge of Erqi, there are few cars and few people. Occasionally I see a person wearing colorful clothes in front of me. I pick up my camera and take a picture. The car drives into the bridge to see that she is still a sanitation worker's eldest sister.

This month, I do not know how many bridges to take Wuhan, each one, are very beautiful.

4 March

Outside the hospital district of Nanjing Road, Wuhan's Central Hospital, the crippled sanitation worker's teacher has been on the go.

The hospital, including Dr. Lee, has lost three doctors to infection with the new coronavirus, and several staff members are in critical condition..

3 March

Yujiahu road, this is not sanitation workers, may be in the road spray disinfection work maintenance personnel.

Sanitation Workers Resting on a curb (I can't remember which road this is...)

26 February

Around the workers'village

Nearby factories, such as Wisco, have been producing.

Near Zhongbei Road, the driver drives a "Beijing sanitation" car. I remember the message of organizing sanitation workers to support Wuhan.

I particularly agree with one suggestion:

Priority should be given to "dispatching" party members from party and government organs, especially those who have the highest "study power" points to come to Wuhan for support. They can not do medical work, but they can help sweep the floor, cleaning should be less of a problem, as it is the best way to test your learning outcomes.

25 February

On Guwen Road, a car sprayed disinfectant on the road.

On this road, there is a small area called "Jiangwan new town" , in mid-early February, an old man who lives here jumped off a building..

On Zhongshan Road, standing on the side of the road, eating lunch.

15 February

The snow was falling

On East L. Road

Wuluo road, ahead, is the Wuhan Yangtze River Bridge

The elder sister and her companion, in the heavy snow, also did not stop working.

Sure, the situation in Wuhan is getting better by the day; of course, there are thirty new cases of pneumonia every day in the last few days, as a medical team friend told me in dismay a few hours before she died in Florida, there was another old man in the hospital they took over..

Cherry blossom, has been the first opening; "victory" , it seems to be in the front.

But don't forget, in this "victory" , there are sanitation workers teachers, an indispensable part.

Because, in the worst days of the epidemic, in the days when the epidemic was getting better, they were always outside their homes, working..

Though he is young, he is willing to be a good memory
